       </h1>
       <div class="homeMainText">
        <h4>
         Angela Vickers, bridal designer has a wonderful collection of over 60 individually styled wedding gowns with an array of shoes, veils, tiaras and jewellery to complement the dresses. Angela and her skilled team also offer a bespoke service where you can experience having an unique design made for you to give a perfect fit for your special day. For a wedding dress as unique as you, visit Angela Vickers Bridal to make dreams come true. Gowns available from £999.
        </h4>
